original_title: Diamondsonmydick & Hi-c - Demons in Tokyo: The Movie
overview: Super rare album that was uploaded briefly and then deleted after the group Reptilian Club Boyz temporarily disbanded. After constant pestering from supporters received to both rappers in the group, they have decided to make available for purchase. All production by Hi-c/C boogie.
